<p class="">I do not want us to stray from the Motion, but I would tell the hon. and gallant Member that some time ago a very careful and thorough investigation was begun touching the very question he has raised, and that it is being carried out at the present time.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
